== 市場營銷 ==
兩張首波劇照於2016年3月14日在《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》上釋出<ref name="USAToday">{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/03/14/ben-hur-movie-sneak-peek/81731732/|title=Sneak peek: Jack Huston takes reins of new 'Ben-Hur'|author=Brian Truitt|work=USA TODAY|date=2016-03-14|accessdate=2016-03-15|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109124824/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/03/14/ben-hur-movie-sneak-peek/81731732/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月15日，今晚娛樂頻道獨家首播了部分戰車場景的片段<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.etonline.com/movies/184595_exclusive_world_premiere_watch_epic_chariot_race_from_the_new_ben_hur/|title=EXCLUSIVE WORLD PREMIERE: Watch Epic Chariot Race From the New 'Ben-Hur'|author=Raphael Chestang|work=Entertainment Tonight|date=2016-03-15|accessdate=2016-03-16|archive-date=2016-03-18|archive-url=https://archive.is/20160318081853/http://m.etonline.com/movies/184595_exclusive_world_premiere_watch_epic_chariot_race_from_the_new_ben_hur/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在隔天在網上釋出了首支官方預告<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/first-ben-hur-reboot-trailer-876172|title=First 'Ben-Hur' Reboot Trailer Arrives|author=Mia Galuppo|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2016-03-16|accessdate=2016-03-17|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212020929/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/first-ben-hur-reboot-trailer-876172|dead-url=no}}</ref>和前導海報<ref>{{cite web|url=http://screenrant.com/ben-hur-2016-trailer-poster/|title=Ben-Hur Trailer & Poster: Stand and Fight|author=Sandy Schaefer|work=''Screenrant''|date=2016-03-16|accessdate=2016-03-17|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109103012/https://screenrant.com/ben-hur-2016-trailer-poster/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該預告也伴隨著已上映一週的《[[科洛弗10號地窖|科洛弗10號地窖]]》播出。

該預告獲得了觀眾和影評人兩極的反應<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11607165|title=New Ben-Hur trailer 'a crime against God'|work=The New Zealand Herald|date=2016-03-17|accessdate=2016-03-17|archive-date=2016-03-18|archive-url=https://archive.is/20160318081834/http://m.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11607165|dead-url=no}}</ref>，認為它和《[[300壯士：帝國崛起|300壯士：帝國崛起]]》<ref name="LYT">{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/lukethompson/2016/03/16/ben-hur-trailer-emphasizes-action-not-jesus/#5a64d0497ba7|title='Ben-Hur' Trailer Emphasizes Action, Not Jesus|author=Luke Y. Thompson|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|date=2016-03-16|accessdate=2016-03-17|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027222035/https://www.forbes.com/sites/lukethompson/2016/03/16/ben-hur-trailer-emphasizes-action-not-jesus/#5a64d0497ba7|dead-url=no}}</ref>、《[[神鬼戰士|神鬼戰士]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.yahoo.com/movies/ben-hur-first-trailer-for-re-do-is-here-160506702.html|title='Ben-Hur': First Trailer for Re-Do Is Here|author=Kevin Polowy|work=Yahoo! Movies|date=2016-03-16|accessdate=2016-03-17|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319113827/https://www.yahoo.com/movies/ben-hur-first-trailer-for-re-do-is-here-160506702.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wired.com/2016/03/ben-hur-trailer/|title=NEW BEN-HUR TRAILER LOOKS LIKE AN EVANGELICAL GLADIATOR|author=K.M. McFaraland|work=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]]|date=2016-03-16|accessdate=2016-03-17|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116002245/https://www.wired.com/2016/03/ben-hur-trailer/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://io9.gizmodo.com/timur-bekmambetovs-ben-hur-remake-is-dumb-loud-and-a-1765270066|title=The Ben-Hur Remake Is Dumb, Loud, and a Crime Against God|author=Rob Bricken|work=''io9''|date=2016-03-17|accessdate=2016-03-18|archive-date=2016-03-18|archive-u